object.customQuery:
select distinct a.systemid, a.PolicyNumber+RIGHT('00'+a.Policyversion,3) as PolicyDisplayNumber,a.PolicyNumber,b.CoverageCd,
       b.Id,b.ParentId,c.SequenceNumber,c.Id as CoverageitemId,c.NumOfUnits as NumOfUnits
from dbo.BasicPolicy_Stg a join dbo.coverage_stg b on a.SystemId = b.SystemId 
left join dbo.Coverageitem_stg c on b.SystemId  =c.SystemId and b.Id = c.ParentId
join dbo.risk_stg(nolock) r on b.SystemId = r.SystemId and b.ParentId = r.id
join dbo.Building_Stg(nolock) s on r.SystemId = s.SystemId and r.id = s.parentid
where a.CMMContainer ='Policy'
  and b.CMMContainer ='Policy'
  and c.CMMContainer ='Policy'
  and r.CMMContainer ='Policy'
  and s.CMMContainer ='Policy'
  and s.BlanketBasisInd='Yes'
and C.Status='Active'
